OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,FIt has taken decades of long, hard
OL,7,Fcampaigning by the bereaved families
OL,8,Fof the Hillsborough victims to get to
OL,9,Fthis point.
OL,11,FNow, 36 years on from the disaster,
OL,12,Fthe Hillsborough Law Bill - which is
OL,13,Falso known as the Public Authority
OL,14,F(Accountability) Bill - will finally
OL,15,Fstart making its way through
OL,16,FParliament.
OL,18,FSo what could the new law look like?
