OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,FThe bill proposes a new professional
OL,7,Fand legal Duty of Candour. This would
OL,8,Frequire public officials to provide
OL,9,Finformation truthfully during
OL,10,Finvestigations and inquiries.
OL,12,FEmma Snell, Legal Policy Manager at
OL,13,Fthe human rights organisation known as
OL,14,FJustice, said: "When public disaster
OL,15,Fstrikes, we obviously want all
OL,16,Ffamilies and victims to be able to get
OL,17,Fthe kind of answers and change that
OL,18,Fthey need and deserve.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
