OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,F"But at the moment, what you see is a
OL,7,Fhuge amount of silence and
OL,8,Fdefensiveness on the part of public
OL,9,Fbodies during investigations and
OL,10,Finquiries into these kind of big
OL,11,Fdisasters like Hillsborough, like
OL,12,FGrenfell."
OL,14,FJust one example of wrongful behaviour
OL,15,Fin the aftermath of the Hillsborough
OL,16,Fdisaster saw some officer's statements
OL,17,Faltered to "mask" police failings.
