OL,6,FMs Snell added: "The duty of candour
OL,7,Fwould change this type of behaviour by
OL,8,Frequiring public servants to act
OL,9,Fopenly and honestly in all of their
OL,10,Fdealings, including in these
OL,11,Finvestigations and inquiries from the
OL,12,Fearliest possible moment."
