OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough families struggled to
OL,7,Ffund their own legal support for
OL,8,Fyears. That was before a Home Office
OL,9,Fscheme stepped in to cover the #63
OL,10,Fmillion fresh inquest costs. This
OL,11,Fensured that the victims' lawyers were
OL,12,Fpaid on the same terms as those
OL,13,Frepresenting the police and other
OL,14,Fstate bodies, creating a fairer
OL,15,Fplaying field.
OL,17,FHowever, as the law stands at the
OL,18,Fminute, most families do not qualify
OL,19,Ffor legal aid in inquests.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
