OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,FMs Snell says that means families can
OL,7,Fturn up at inquests "and be met by a
OL,8,Fkind of cadre of state lawyers, which
OL,9,Fis obviously very intimidating...
OL,11,F"But also makes it very difficult for
OL,12,Fthem to get the answers that they need
OL,13,Fwhen they don't have someone who has
OL,14,Fthe training to be able to get past
OL,15,Fsome of that defensiveness."
OL,17,FThe new law proposes to put an end to
OL,18,Fthis practise by providing non-means
OL,19,Ftested help and support for inquests.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
