OL,3,CHillsborough Law Bill finally laid
OL,4,Cbefore Parliament but what is it?
OL,6,FHe added: "The Hillsborough families
OL,7,Fwill never see true justice done for
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones. But because of their
OL,9,Ftenacity, dignity and refusal to be
OL,10,Fsilenced, no other bereaved families
OL,11,Fwill ever have to endure the same
OL,12,Fordeal. That is their legacy ` and it
OL,13,Fwill stand for generations to come."
